# Caddyfile for HollerithEnergyML.
#
# SITE_DOMAIN is injected from /etc/hollerith/.env via env_file on the caddy
# service; if unset the placeholder domain is used so the file still parses
# cleanly during local validation.

{$SITE_DOMAIN:hollerith.example.de} {
	encode zstd gzip

	header {
		Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload"
		X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
		X-Frame-Options "DENY"
		Referrer-Policy "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
		Permissions-Policy "camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()"
		Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self' data:; connect-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'"
		-Server
	}

	@api path /api/*

	handle @api {
		reverse_proxy api:8000
	}

	handle {
		reverse_proxy web:3000
	}

	log {
		output stdout
		format json
		level INFO
	}
}
